      "widgets_values": [
        "=== SUPIR Multi-GPU Video Upscaler with Fidelity ===\n\nFIDELITY PRESETS:\n- full_fidelity: Maximum skin/lighting/detail\n- skin_realistic: Natural pores, subsurface\n- lighting_enhanced: Professional lighting\n- facial_detail: Sharp eyes, contours\n\nGPU SELECTION:\n- cuda:0 = RTX 3090 (24GB)\n- cuda:1 = RTX 3060 (12GB)\n\nMEMORY TIPS:\n- Pre-resize to 768px for RTX 3060\n- tiled_vae = true saves memory\n- PurgeVRAM nodes free GPU memory\n\nSETTINGS:\n- Steps: 15 (fast) to 30 (quality)\n- CFG: 4.0 (balanced fidelity)\n- control_scale: 1.0 (faithful)"
